\define reference-agent-widget()
<$tiddlywiki-reference-agent-widget />
\end

Allows you to specify multiple tiddler references and custom instructions for an AI agent. The widget also supports generating content to a target tiddler.

Features:
* Select multiple tiddlers as references for the agent
* Provide custom instructions for how the agent should use the references
* Optionally specify a target tiddler where content will be generated
* Choose whether to append to or overwrite the target tiddler
* Export conversations to a separate tiddler

```
<<reference-agent-widget>>
``` 